text.tspan: Knowledge Gate (KG) is an unique online education platform of its class for the
Computer Science /Information Technology/(CS/IT) Students, either those who
are seeking a bright carrier directly industry (private or government) or those
who are dreaming for the best possible carrer & are willing to appear in GATE
We provide online classes, online test series & postal course
material to the students. We have dedicated team which work
round the clock in the benefit of the students.
